    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make spiking an indictable offence with minimum of 3 months prison and area bans",
        "additional_details": "There are many reports on the news about individuals being spiked within the night-time economy. Making spiking an indictable offence could help deter people from doing it and increase the number of people who report it to the police.",
        "background": "Spiking should be an indictable offence with a minimum sentence of 3 months, which increases with repeat offending. Area banning orders should also be used. This could help root out repeat offenders and keep our nightlife as safe as possible. ",
